OL,3,CMan who survived cancer as a child and
OL,4,Cadult organises charity ball
OL,6,FA man from Greater Manchester who
OL,7,Flived through cancer as a child, and
OL,8,Fagain as a young adult, has organised
OL,9,Fa grand charity ball to help others
OL,10,Ffacing the disease.
OL,12,FHamish Graham, from Littleborough near
OL,13,FRochdale, hopes his football and film-
OL,14,Fthemed event will raise money for two
OL,15,Fcharities helping teenage cancer
OL,16,Fpatients.
OL,18,FHamish was just 23 when he began
OL,19,Ffeeling dizzy and tired back in May
OL,20,F2020. His family also noticed he had
OL,21,Flost a lot of weight.
