OL,3,CMan who survived cancer as a child and
OL,4,Cadult organises charity ball
OL,6,FAt an in initial appointment at an out-
OL,7,Fof-hours GP practice, Hamish was told
OL,8,Fhe likely had a migraine.
OL,10,FHowever, his mum Sarah, 57, pushed for
OL,11,Fa blood test which later revealed he
OL,12,Fhad leukaemia, a blood cancer which
OL,13,Fdevelops in the bone marrow or
OL,14,Flymphatic system.
OL,16,FHamish endured three years of
OL,17,Fchemotherapy before finally going into
OL,18,Fremission in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
