OL,3,CMan who survived cancer as a child and
OL,4,Cadult organises charity ball
OL,6,FIt wasn't the first time the family
OL,7,Fhave experienced a health shock,
OL,8,FHamish was diagnosed with a rare brain
OL,9,Ftumour when he was just seven years
OL,10,Fold.
OL,12,FHe went through six weeks of
OL,13,Fradiotherapy and 18 months of
OL,14,Fchemotherapy before eventually being
OL,15,Fgiven the all-clear.
OL,17,FHamish, who works at the ODEON cinema
OL,18,Fin the Trafford Centre, can recall the
OL,19,Ffirst symptom he showed right before
OL,20,Fhis second diagnosis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
