OL,3,CMan who survived cancer as a child and
OL,4,Cadult organises charity ball
OL,6,F"I just felt tired and I couldn't go
OL,7,Fany further. My mum then tried to get
OL,8,Fme in for a blood test."
OL,10,F"It just felt like deja vu because I'd
OL,11,Fbeen through it once before. It got me
OL,12,Fdown a bit. I feel okay now and am
OL,13,Flooking forward to getting back to
OL,14,Fspeed with work. I still work now, but
OL,15,Fnot as many hours as I used to, but
OL,16,FI'm getting there."
OL,18,FSarah, says Hamish's recent leukaemia
OL,19,Fdiagnosis brought back bad memories
OL,20,Ffrom when he was a child.
