OL,3,CMan who survived cancer as a child and
OL,4,Cadult organises charity ball
OL,6,F"It was quite traumatic for both of
OL,7,Fus, I think a lot of the stuff from
OL,8,Fthe first battle resurfaced and the
OL,9,Fstuff we had to deal with, especially
OL,10,Fbeing in isolation, brought everything
OL,11,Fback up.
OL,13,F"One of the good things was that some
OL,14,Fof the staff that treated Hamish when
OL,15,Fhe was seven were still there."
OL,17,FHaving battled cancer twice, Hamish is
OL,18,Fnow set to raise cash for the
OL,19,Fcharities that have supported him over
OL,20,Fthe years.
