OL,4,Cadult organises charity ball
OL,6,FHe has created MARVELous night out, an
OL,7,Fevent which will take place at The
OL,8,FEdwardian hotel in Manchester city
OL,9,Fcentre on September 28 in aid of The
OL,10,FTeenage Cancer Trust and The Christie
OL,11,FTeenage and Young Adult Unit.
OL,13,F"Hamish's MARVELous Night Out is our
OL,14,Fbiggest fundraising mission yet,"
OL,15,FSarah added.
OL,17,F"Hamish has already raised over
OL,18,F#38,000 for charity and we hope that
OL,19,Fthis event will propel that total much
OL,20,Fhigher.
