OL,4,Cadult organises charity ball
OL,6,F"We're extremely grateful for the
OL,7,Fsupport of all those involved, the
OL,8,Fcommunity has really come together and
OL,9,Fthe support from Manchester City
OL,10,Fsupporters shows that there is no
OL,11,Frivalry when it comes to helping
OL,12,Fworthy causes."
OL,14,FHosted by Hits Radio presenter Mike
OL,15,FToolan, the evening will feature a
OL,16,Flive band, a DJ set, a silent auction
OL,17,Fwith 'money can't buy' prizes, a
OL,18,Fdrinks reception, a raffle, and more.
OL,19,FHamish's MARVELous Night Out will also
OL,20,Ffeature his two favourite things `
OL,21,Ffilms and football.
